    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    Config
    Configuration object for TypeTagsWeaver instances.
    Config.Builder
    Builder for Config instances.
    Example
     
    PhoneNumber
    Annotates declarations of type String for which the value, if non-null, must be valid E.164 phone number.
    PhoneNumber.Validator
    Validator for the @PhoneNumber annotation.
    TypeRestrictionException
    Specialization of ClassCastException thrown by TypeTagValidator.validate() to indicate that a value is invalid because of its actual value rather than simply by having the wrong Java type.
    TypeTag
    Meta-annotation for type annotations that can be validated at compile time and runtime by TypeTags.
    TypeTagRuntime
    Runtime functionality required by the bytecode modifications applied by the TypeTagsWeaver.
    TypeTagsWeaver
    Weaves runtime checks for TypeTags.
    TypeTagValidator
    Implemented by classes capable of runtime validation of values whose types are annotated with a @TypeTag meta-annotated annotation.
    TypeUtil
    Utility methods.
